OL,3,CWhat we have learned from the Peter
OL,4,CMandelson files
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer, Kieran
OL,7,FCarter
OL,9,FDetails of Lord Mandelson's
OL,10,Fappointment and subsequent removal as
OL,11,FUS ambassador were revealed on
OL,12,FWednesday in the release of nearly 150
OL,13,Ffiles by the government.
OL,15,FThe publication of the documents was
OL,16,Fforced by MPs, amid questions over
OL,17,Fwhat was known about the peer's links
OL,18,Fto paedophile financier Jeffrey
OL,19,FEpstein before he was handed the
OL,20,FWashington job.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
