CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773324680
OL,3,CWhat we have learned from the Peter
OL,4,CMandelson files
OL,6,FThe files included due diligence and
OL,7,Fadvice provided to Sir Keir Starmer
OL,8,Fbefore the December 2024 appointment,
OL,9,Fin which he was warned of reputational
OL,10,Frisks, as well as papers and meeting
OL,11,Fminutes on Lord Mandelson taking up
OL,12,Fthe job, and on his September 2025
OL,13,Fsacking and severance payout.
OL,15,FMandelson has previously apologised
OL,16,Ffor his relationship with Epstein,
OL,17,Fclaiming he did not witness wrongdoing
OL,18,Fin his interactions with the
OL,19,Fpaedophile and "deeply regrets"
OL,20,Fcontinuing his relationship for so
OL,21,Flong.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
