OL,3,CWhat we have learned from the Peter
OL,4,CMandelson files
OL,6,FIn relation to his arrest on suspicion
OL,7,Fof misconduct in public office, the
OL,8,Fformer ambassador has claimed not to
OL,9,Fhave acted in any way criminally.
OL,11,FFurther files are expected to be
OL,12,Freleased at a later date, once police
OL,13,Fdecide they no longer pose a risk of
OL,14,Fprejudice to their ongoing
OL,15,Finvestigation into Mandelson.
OL,17,FSo what do the documents show, and how
OL,18,Fdamaging are they?
OL,20,FPeter Mandelson requested severance
OL,21,Fpay of nearly #550,000
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
