OL,3,CWhat we have learned from the Peter
OL,4,CMandelson files
OL,6,FFollowing his sacking as US
OL,7,Fambassador, documents show Mandelson
OL,8,Finitially asked to be paid for the
OL,9,Fremainder of his four-year fixed-term
OL,10,Fcontract.
OL,12,FThis amounted to #547,201.
OL,14,FHe was eventually paid a package of
OL,15,Fnearly #75,000, made up of #40,330 as
OL,16,Fpay in lieu of notice, and a special
OL,17,Fseverance payment of #34,670.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
