OL,3,CWhat we have learned from the Peter
OL,4,CMandelson files
OL,6,FAddressing MPs on Wednesday,
OL,7,Fgovernment minister Darren Jones
OL,8,Fclaimed the government, "wouldn't have
OL,9,Fwanted to pay one pound to Peter
OL,10,FMandelson", but claimed the government
OL,11,Fhad been advised the cost of an
OL,12,Femployment tribunal and subsequent
OL,13,Fpayment could have reached much higher
OL,14,Fthan the eventual near #75,000 payment
OL,15,Fthat was settled on.
OL,17,FJones went on to explain that while
OL,18,Fgovernment ministers can be removed
OL,19,Ffrom post without recourse to an
OL,20,Femployment tribunal, civil servants
OL,21,Foperate under regular employment law.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
