OL,3,CWhat we have learned from the Peter
OL,4,CMandelson files
OL,6,FThe same document shows Mandelson
OL,7,Fbelieved the contractual obligation of
OL,8,Fthree months severance was
OL,9,F"insufficient", as "they believe the
OL,10,Factions of His Majesty's Government
OL,11,Fhave permanently damaged their
OL,12,Femployability."
OL,14,FDifficulty viewing these images? Click
OL,15,Fhere to open in browser.
OL,17,FMandelson was appointed as ambassador
OL,18,Fand received "high-tier" briefings
OL,19,Fbefore vetting was complete
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
