OL,3,CWhat we have learned from the Peter
OL,4,CMandelson files
OL,6,FAlthough not unusual for certain
OL,7,Froles, the documents released on
OL,8,FWednesday also show Lord Mandelson was
OL,9,Foffered the post of ambassador, before
OL,10,Fcompleting the official vetting
OL,11,Fprocess.
OL,13,FOn December 20, 2024, the Foreign,
OL,14,FCommonwealth and Development Office
OL,15,F(FCDO), emailed Mandelson saying:
OL,16,F"Congratulations on your appointment
OL,17,Fas HMA Washington and welcome to the
OL,18,FFCDO."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773324680
OL,3,CWhat we have learned from the Peter
OL,4,CMandelson files
OL,6,FThis email also said: "I'd also be
OL,7,Fgrateful if you could return the
OL,8,Fattached conflict of interest form as
OL,9,Fsoon as possible," implying Mandleson
OL,10,Fwas yet to do so.
OL,12,FIt is not until December 23, however,
OL,13,Fthat he receives an email explaining
OL,14,Fwhat "the most important first steps
OL,15,Fwill be," one of which includes "going
OL,16,Fthrough the vetting process".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
