OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773324680
OL,3,CWhat we have learned from the Peter
OL,4,CMandelson files
OL,6,FThe email also reveals Mandelson would
OL,7,Fbe briefed "further in person from
OL,8,FJanuary 6 onwards, including atJhigher
OL,9,Ftiers," 23 days before it is first
OL,10,Fconfirmed he has passed security
OL,11,Fclearance.
OL,13,FOn January 27, three days before the
OL,14,FFCDO confirmed Mandelson had passed
OL,15,Fthe relevant security clearance with
OL,16,Fthe vetting team, Permanent Under-
OL,17,FSecretary at the FCDO, Olly Robbins,
OL,18,Fwrote to Mandelson asking if he should
OL,19,F"get the wheels in motion for Peter's
OL,20,Faudience' with the King."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
