OL,3,CWhat we have learned from the Peter
OL,4,CMandelson files
OL,6,FIt isn't until three days later that
OL,7,FMandelson is emailed confirmation that
OL,8,Fhe passed the security clearance with
OL,9,Fthe vetting team.
OL,11,FThe PM was warned he would be left
OL,12,F"more exposed" if Mandelson was
OL,13,Foffered the ambassador role
OL,15,FIn 2024, Starmer sought advice on his
OL,16,Foptions for filling the US ambassador
OL,17,Fposition.
OL,19,FHe was told the incumbent ambassador,
OL,20,FKaren Pearce, had "made good inroads"
OL,21,Fwith the incoming Trump administration.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
