OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773324680
OL,3,CWhat we have learned from the Peter
OL,4,CMandelson files
OL,6,FHe was then warned that while a
OL,7,Fpolitical appointment would create a
OL,8,Fstrong link to both him and his
OL,9,Fgovernment's priorities, it also
OL,10,Fcarried increased risk.
OL,12,F"If anything goes wrong, you could be
OL,13,Fmore exposed as the individual is more
OL,14,Fconnected to you personally," the
OL,15,Fadvice stated.
OL,17,FStarmer was also warned in specific
OL,18,Fadvice relating to Peter Mandelson
OL,19,Fthat several conflicts of interest,
OL,20,Fincluding his relationship with
OL,21,FEpstein, risked "reputational damage".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
