OL,3,CWhat we have learned from the Peter
OL,4,CMandelson files
OL,6,FThe PM was told in 2024 Mandelson
OL,7,Fstayed at Epstein's apartment while he
OL,8,Fwas in prison for child sex offences
OL,10,FIn advice given to the prime minister
OL,11,Fin December 2024, while considering
OL,12,FMandelson's appointment, Starmer was
OL,13,Ftold that a 2019 report commissioned
OL,14,Fby JP Morgan had found Epstein
OL,15,Fappeared to "maintain a particularly
OL,16,Fclose relationship with Prince Andrew,
OL,17,Fthe Duke of York, and Lord Peter
OL,18,FMandelson, a senior member of the
OL,19,FBritish government."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
