OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773324680
OL,3,CWhat we have learned from the Peter
OL,4,CMandelson files
OL,6,FAs part of this advice, the prime
OL,7,Fminister was told Mandelson had stayed
OL,8,Fat Epstein's New York house in 2009
OL,9,Fwhile the convicted paedophile was
OL,10,Fserving a jail sentence for procuring
OL,11,Fan underage girl.
OL,13,FThis advice also included several
OL,14,Fother facts about Mandelson's
OL,15,Frelationship with both Epstein and
OL,16,FGhislane Maxwell, including his links
OL,17,Fto a charity founded by the latter.
OL,19,FPM's national security adviser,
OL,20,FJonathan Powell found Mandelson's
OL,21,Fappointment "weirdly rushed"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
