OL,3,CWhat we have learned from the Peter
OL,4,CMandelson files
OL,6,FA summary of a fact-finding call
OL,7,Fbetween National Security Adviser
OL,8,FJonathan Powell and the prime
OL,9,Fminister's general counsel showed
OL,10,FPowell thought Mandelson's appointment
OL,11,Fhas been "weirdly rushed".
OL,13,FJonathan Powell had raised these
OL,14,Fconcerns with the PM's then chief of
OL,15,Fstaff Morgan McSweeney, but was told
OL,16,Fby the latter, these concerns had been
OL,17,Faddressed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
