OL,3,CWhat we have learned from the Peter
OL,4,CMandelson files
OL,6,FThe junior foreign office minister at
OL,7,Fthe time was Philli Barton, and Powell
OL,8,Fnoted he also held reservations around
OL,9,FMandelson's appointment.
